\id 1JN 1JHN - Ndwewe Bible Version 
\h Yohane 
\toc1 Nhalo ghwa Maha handa paghutyekitwe na 
\toc2 1 YOHANE 
\toc3 1Yhn 
\mt2 Nhalo ghwa Maha handa paghutyekitwe na 
\mt1 1 YOHANE 
\imt1 Ulongoleho 
\ip Lihamba lya 1 Yohane likitekwa na Nndumilwa Yohane mu pakati ya ngungwa hya 85 na 90 mbole ya kubhelekwa Yesu Kilisto. Yohane kangulikambuha ng'obhe kukita ywombe ndo ywakatyekite lihamba ali, Peni kipalamande kya ulongohi kingummoneha kukita ywombe handa ywakabhonite na kakilibhonela kwa meho ghake ubhumi na kuhyuka kwa Yesu Kilisto, kipalamande kya 1 Yohana 1:1-3. Bhubho madolido gha matyekelo ghangulihwana muno na ghala ghaakumokoleka mu Nhalo ghwa Maha handa mughutyekitwe na Yohane. Yinguhyubhalika kukita Yohane ndo ywakatyekite Nhalo ghwa Maha handa mughutyekitwe na Yohane mu mahamba ghala mandatu, ghene ndo 1 Yohane na 2 Yohane na 3 Yohane manjubha ghene yohane kakibhegha kangutama mu kitami kya akwo Efeso. 
\ip Yohane kakityeka lihamba ali kwa Akilisito bhoha mu manjubha ghene lingwemuko lya bhandu bhaanhyubhalila Kilisto likitindilwa na mangolombano ghaabhukaniti na bhandu bhaalikemite “Awagunositi.” Bhandu abho bhakihyubhalila kukita Yesu kakibhegha Chapanga ntwihiliko peni kakibhegha chepa mundu menyu pakabheghite kangutama pannima. Kubhukana na nnando aghwo Yohane kakilikambuka kukita ywombe ndo mundu ywakabhonite ubhumi ghwa Yesu kwa meho ghake, na kwa mabhoko ghake mwene bhubho kakinbyala Yesu, kipalamande kya 1 Yohana 1:1-3. Ningo ya Yohane ya kutyeka lihamba ali ghakibhegha ndo kutwihiliha uyelelo ghwake ywombe, kipalamande kya 1 Yohana 1:4, kuakanikiha ahyubhalila akotoke kutenda ulemwa kipalamande kya Yohana 2:1, kubhakanikiha bhaanhyubhalila Kilisto akotoke kutughila mahundo gha uhwangi, kipalamande kya 1 Yohana 2:26, na kuapegha ubhoneho ghwa kumanya kya kulyaghila kukita bhombe ahyubhalila alopoleghwa, kipalamande kya 1 Yohana 5:13. 
\iot Ghaabheghite 
\io1 Yohane kanguyanda lihamba lyake, bhubho kangulubhulila ningo yimu ya kulityeka lihamba ali kipalamande kya 1 Yohana 1:1-4. 
\io1 Mbole, kangufwambula bhula Chapanga pakabhegha lung'ali na kutusigha kukita tungunoghwa kutama handa Yesu pakatamite munnima, kipalamande kya 1 Yohane 1:5—3:10. 
\io1 Kangi kangutukulungwa kwakya ngwiliho ya kupalana twenga kwa twenga, kipalamande kya 1 Yohana 3:11—5:12. 
\io1 Paul kanguyomolela lihamba lyake mu kipalamande kya 5:13-21. 
\c 1  
\s1 Lilagho lya Ubhumi 
\p  
\v 1 Twenga tungaalandamiha mihalo ya yula, Lilagho lya Ubhumi, kakibhegha kutandila makachu, twenga andumilwa tukinnyihwa na tukimmona kwa meho ghetu, na kunkamula kwa mabhoko ghetu.  
\v 2 Ndo ywombe ywakabhegha Ubhumi, kakibhoneka kwa twenga. Tukimmona na habhu tunguhola kuaghombela bhangi yakya mihalo yake. Hunu tungualubhulila mihalo kukita ywombe ndo ubhumi ghwa manjubha ghoha ywkabheghite na Chapanga Tate na kakibhonekana kwa twenga.  
\v 3 Tungulandamiha Nhalo ghwa Yesu aywo, ywene tukimmona na kunnyihwa, ili mmeghe papamu na twenga mu ughumu ghwene ghutubheghite naghwo na Tate Chapanga na Mwana ywake Yesu Kilisto.  
\v 4 Tunguatyekela mwenga milando ayi ili tuyelelwe kyanalumu. 
\s1 Chapanga ndo ulangalo 
\p  
\v 5 Hino, nhalo ghutughuyihwite kuhuma kwa Yesu na ghutubhalandamiha ndo aghu, kukita Chapanga ndo ywa maha na ywa nyanyi na lung'ali na kahone lubhindo lyohele nkati mwake.  
\v 6 Patulongela kukita tubhegha papamu na Chapanga, na kunu tungughendelela kutama mu lubhindo, tungubhegha ahwangi na tungutama ng'obhe mu hoto kwa malagho na mandendelo.  
\v 7 Peni handa twaatama mu lulangalo, handa mwene pakabhegha mu lulangalo, ndo twaabhegha na ughumo twenga kwa twenga na mwahi ghwa Mwana ghwaki Yesu Kilisto, ghwatuyoha ulemwa ghwoha. 
\p  
\v 8 Patulongela kukita twaabhegha ng'obhe ulemwa, apwo tungulikuluha twabhene, na kahone hoto mu twenga.  
\v 9 Handa patulongela na kulilipetula ulemwa ghwetu, Chapanga katatulekekeha ulemwa ghwetu na kutughulula kuhuma mu uhakata ghwoha kiyaha ywombe nhyubhaliko na kabhegha na kangutenda ghanakunoghela.  
\v 10 Handa patulongela kukita tunatenda ng'obhe ulemwa, tunguntenda Chapanga nhwangi na tungulema mahundo ghake. 
\c 2  
\s1 Kilisto ntangatila ghwetu 
\p  
\v 1 Bhana bhangu, nunguatyekela mihalo ayi ili nkotoke kutenda ulemwa. Peni handa mundu ywohele pakatenda ulemwa, tubhegha na nnyupila gwetu kwa Tate, aywo ndo Yesu Kilisto, ywakayitikilwa muulongolo ghwa Chapanga.  
\v 2 Ywombe Kilisto ndo nyambi ywkabhuha ulemwa ghwetu, chepa ulemwa ghwetu ghweka, ngati ndo ulemwa ghwa bhandu bhoha. 
\p  
\v 3 Handa patuyitikila malaghilo gha Chapanga, twahotola kubhegha na ulyaghilo kukita tungummanya.  
\v 4 Mundu ywohele ywakalongela, “Nungummanya Chapanga” Peni kanguyitikila ng'obhe malaghilo ghake, anywo kangukuluha, na kahone hoto nkati yake.  
\v 5 Peni mundu ywohele ywakayihwa na kuyitikila mahundo ghake, kulyaghila upalo ghwa Chapanga ghubhegha tela nkati yake. Mu alyo tungumanya kukita tubhegha nkati yake.  
\v 6 Ywohele ywaalongela kabhegha papamu na Chapanga, kangunoghwa katame handa pakatamite Yesu. 
\s1 Ngwliho ya hyono 
\p  
\v 7 Maaghanja bhangu bhanuapala, ngwilho yinubhatyekela chepa ya hyono ngati ndo yila ya makachu, yila yimmeghite naywo kutandila makachu. Ngwiliho ayi ya makachu ndo lila lilagho lilimuyihwite.  
\v 8 Kangi ngwilho ayi yinubhatyekela ndo ya hyono, uhoto ghwake ghungubhonekana bhula Yesu Kilisto pakabheghite kangutama na mumatamilo ghenu, kiyaha lubhindo lungupita na lung'ali lya hoto lungung'ala. 
\p  
\v 9 Mundu ywohele ywakalongela kangutama mu lulangalo peni kangunkikinalila nnongo ghwake aywo kabhegha kakali kangutama mulubhindo.  
\v 10 Mundu ywohele ywakanpala nnyake kangutama mu lulangalo, na kahone kilibhi kyohele kiihotola kunnyambuha kutenda ulemwa.  
\v 11 Peni ywohele ywakankalalila nnyake, kangutama mu lubhindo na kangutyanga mulubhindo, kangi lubhindo lubhegha totolo mu meho ghake, Kiyaha lubhindo luntenda kahotole ng'obhe kubhona. 
\p  
\v 12 Nunguatyekela mwenga, bhana adoko, kiyaha Chapanga kabhalekekeha ulemwa ghwenu kupitila Yesu Kilisto.  
\v 13 Nunguatyekela mwenga, maakina tate, kiyaha mummanya Yesu Kilisto ywene ywakabheghite kutandila makachu. Nunguatyekela mwenga ahongolo kiyaha munhotola yula Nchipila  
\v 14 Nunguatyekela mwenga mabhana, kiyaha mungummanya Chapanga Tate. Nunguatyekela mwenga maakina tate, kiyaha mungummanya Yesu Kilisto ywakabheghite kutandila makechu, nunguatyekela mwenga ahongolo kiyaha mmegha na makakala, munguliyitikila lilagho lya Chapanga, kangi munhotola yula Nchipila. 
\p  
\v 15 Nkotoke kutenda milando mihokelo, handa bhandu bhanga kummanya Chapanga. Nkotoke kuhipala hyoha hyaahipala, mundu ywakapala uhakata ghwa nnima, Chapanga kangumpala ng'obhe mundu aywo.  
\v 16 Uhokelo ghwa pannima ndo aghu, tama ya mmili, tama ya kila kighukibhona na kulilokela hilibhi hitubheghite nahyo, hyoha ahi hingubhuka ng'obhe kwa Tate ngati hinguhuma mu nnima aghu.  
\v 17 Naghwo nnima ghungupita papamu na tama hyake hyoha hakataho, peni yula ywakatenda ghala ghaghaapala Chapanga katatama manjubha ghoha. 
\s1 Apingika bha Kilisto 
\p  
\v 18 Maabhana achoko, agha ndo manjubha gha uhiko! Handa pannyihwa kukita npingika ghwa Kilisto kanguhika, habhu, apingika bha Kilisto atangala bhahika kala. Kubhukana na agho tungumanya kukita manjubha agha ndo manjubha gha muuhiko.  
\v 19 Bhandu abho bhakihuma kwa twenga, peni kulyaghila bhakibhegha ng'obhe papamu na twenga. Kiyaha handa bhangabheghite papamu na twenga, bhangatamite papamu na twenga, peni kiyaha bhabhuka, yingubhoneha kukita kahone hata yumu ywabhe ywakabheghite papamu na twenga. 
\p  
\v 20 Peni mwenga munnyitikila Nhuki ghwa Chapanga ywene Kilisto kakiapopokeha, hinu munguumanya uhoto ghwa Chapanga.  
\v 21 Nunguatyekela ng'obhe kiyaha munguyimanya ng'obhe hoto, ngati kiyaha munguyimaha hoto, na mwenga mungumanya kukita kahone uhwangi ghughuhuma mu hoto. 
\p  
\v 22 Nhwangi ndo ghani? Ndo yula ywakalongela kukita Yesu ndo chepa Kilisto. Mundu ywa habhu ndo npingika ghwa Kilisto, na aywo kangunlema Tate Chapanga na Yesu Mwana ywake.  
\v 23 Kiyaha ywohele ywakannema Mwana, aywo kangunnema na Tate, na ywohele ywakankingama Mwana, aywo kangunkingama na Tate bhubho. 
\p  
\v 24 Hinu, nng'endelele kughakamula ghala ghamughayihwite kutandila makachu ghangutama nkati ya mwenga. Na handa ghala ghamughayihwite kutandila makachu ghangutama nkati yenu, na mwenga maaghendelela kubhegha na ughumu na Mwana na Tate.  
\v 25 Nnaghilo yakatulaghite twenga ndo ayi, ubhumi ghwa manjubha ghoha. 
\p  
\v 26 Nunguatyekela milando ayi kualinga bhala bhaayighite kubhakuluha mwenga.  
\v 27 Peni kwa mwenga, Chapanga kabhapegha Nhuki ghwake, ywene kangutama nkati yenu, Aywo ndo kanguahunda ghoha, chepa uhwangi. Kya habhu yingunoghwa ng'obhe kukita mundu kabhahunde. Handa bhula Nhuki kabhahunda, hinu nng'endelele kubhegha mpapamu na Kilisto. 
\p  
\v 28 Hinu, mabhana bhangu, nng'endelele kubhegha papamu na Kilisto, ili pakapala kubhuya tubheghe akangamalo kyanga kulihiha na kubhona honi mulijubha lya kuhika kwa ywombe.  
\v 29 Handa pammanya kukita Kilisto kakitenda ghanakunnogheha Chapanga bubho mungumanya bhoha bhanakutenda ghanakunnogheha Chapanga abhegha bha maha. 
\c 3  
\s1 Twenga ndo bhana bha Chapanga 
\p  
\v 1 Nnole, ndo upalo ghwakya bhuli ghwakatupeghite Tate, kukita twenga tukemwe bhana bha Chapanga, habhu ndo mutubhegha. Kya habhu bhandu bhangannyitikila Changapanga bhangutumanya ng'obhe, kiyaha bhangummanya ng'obhe ywombe.  
\v 2 Apalo bhangu, hinu twenga ndo bhana bha Chapanga. Chapanga kanatubhoneha ng'obhe bhula mutupala kubhegha manjubha paghapala kuhika. Peni tungumanya kukita pakapala kuhika kangi Kilisto, tutalihwana na ywombe. Tutammona handa mukabheghite.  
\v 3 Ywohele ywakalidumbila ali kangughululika na kulibhika nyanyi muulongolo ghwa Chapanga handa bhula Kilisto mwakabhegha. 
\p  
\v 4 Ywohele ywakatenda ulemwa kanguyitikila ng'obhe malaghilo gha Chapanga, kiyaha ulemwa ndo kulema kuyitikila malaghilo gha Chapanga.  
\v 5 Mungumanya kukita Kilisto kakihika kughubhuha ulemwa ghwetu, na kangi ywombe Kilisto kabhegha ng'obhe na ulemwa.  
\v 6 Ywohele ywakabhegha papamu na Kilisto kangughendelela ng'obhe kutenda ulemwa. Peni ywohele ywakatenda ulemwa, kammona ng'obhe ywombe ebu kummanya Kilisto ndo ghani. 
\p  
\v 7 Basi, bhana apalo, nkotoke kupotohwa na mundu ywohele. Ywohele ywakatenda milando yinakunnogheha Chapanga kanguyitikilwa na Chapanga, kabhegha ywa maha handa Kilisto pakayitikilwa na Chapanga.  
\v 8 Peni ywakatenda ulemwa ndo ywa Nchipila, kiyaha Nchipila katenda ulemwa kutandila makachu. Na kwa kihokonyo aki Mwana ywa Chapanga kakihika ili kakalikanjaghane lihengo lya Nchipila. 
\p  
\v 9 Kila ywakabhegha mwana ghwa Chapanga kangutenda ng'obhe ulemwa, kiyaha kabhegha na matamilo gha hyono nkati yake, ywombe kangutenda ng'obhe ulemwa, kiyaha ywombe mwana ghwa Chapanga.  
\v 10 Kya habhu, mundu ywohele ywakatenda ng'obhe milando yakayipala Chapanga, ebu ywakampala ng'obhe nnyake, aywo ndo mwana ghwa Nchipila. 
\s1 Mulipale 
\p  
\v 11 Llilagho limliyihwite kutandila makachu ndo ali, kukita tungunoghwa kila mundu kampale nnyake.  
\v 12 Nkotoke kubhegha handa Kaini kakilongohwa na yula Nhokelo, kakinkoma nnongo ghake. Hinu, kiyaha niki kakinkoma nnongo ywake? Kakinkoma kiyaha ndendelo yake yikibha hakata na ndendelo ya nnongo ywake yikibhegha ya maha. 
\p  
\v 13 Basi alongo bhangu, nkotoke kukangacha handa bhandu bhangannyitikila Chapanga paabhakalalila.  
\v 14 Twenga tungumanya kukita tuhuma mu makakala gha kiho na kuyingila muubhumi, kiyaha tunguapala alongo. Ywohele ywanga kunpala nnongo ghwaki kangutama mu kiho.  
\v 15 Ywohele ywakankalalila nnyake ndo nkoma bhandu, na mwenga mungumanya kukita yunakuma bhandu kabhegha ng'obhe na ubhumi ghwa manjubha ghoha nkati yake.  
\v 16 Kya habhu, twahotola kughumanya upalo ghwa Chapanga, kiyaha Yesu Kilisto kakighubhuha ubhumi ghwake kwakya twenga. Na twenga tungunoghwa kughubhuha ubhumi ghwetu kwakya abho alongo bhetu ahyubhaliala.  
\v 17 Handa mundu kabhegha na hilibhi ngenju hya apa pannima na nnongo ghwake kabhegha ng'obhe na hilibhi, peni kabhegha na mwoyo nnonopo ghwa kummonele luhungu nnyake, kaahotola kulongela kangumpala Chapanga?  
\v 18 Bhana apalo, tukotoke kupala kwa malagho ebu kwa ngulu ngati kwa ndendelo na hoto. 
\s1 Ghwangebhegha na lyogha muulongolo ghwa Chapanga 
\p  
\v 19 Habhu ndo mutuhotola kumanya kya hoto kukita twenga ndo bhandu bha ghuhoto, na twaabhegha ng'obhe na lyogha muulongolo ghwa Chapanga.  
\v 20 Kiyaha hata patulitosite twabhene mu myoyo yetu, kukita tubhegha na ulemwa, tungubhegha na uhihimilo, kiyaha Chapanga kangumanya ghoha.  
\v 21 Alongo bhangu apalo, handa myoyo yetu yingututosa ng'obhe kukita tubhegha na uhokelo, basi, tungubhegha na ukangamalo muulongolo ghwa Chapanga,  
\v 22 na kupokela kuhuma kwa Chapanga kilibhi kitukiyupa, kiyaha tughayitikila hilo ghake na kughatenda ghala ghakaghapala.  
\v 23 Na ngwiliho yake ndo ayi, kukita tunhyubhalile Mwana ghwake Yesu Kilisto, na tulipale twabhene handa pakatukwilikihite.  
\v 24 Bhala bhoha bhaayitikila ngwiliho hya Chapanga bhangutama mu kulungana na Chapanga na Chapanga mu kulungana naywo. Twenga tungumanya kukita kangutama mu kulungana na twenga. 
\c 4  
\s1 Nhuki ghwa hoto na nhuki ghwa uhwangi 
\p  
\v 1 Maalongo bhangu bhanuapala, nkotoke kuhyubhalila kila mundu ywakalongela kabhegha na Nhuki ywa Chapanga, ngati muyihingukihe mihuki aywo ngati muhotole kumanya kukita yihuma kwa Chapanga, kiyaha ambuye atangalo ghwa uhwangi abwituka mu nnima.  
\v 2 Ayi ndo njila ya kumanya handa mundu kangulongohwa na Nhuki ghwa Chapanga, ywohele ywakakambuka kukita Kilisto kakihika na kakibhegha, kakibhegha handa mundu, mundu aywo kabhegha na Nhuki ghwa Chapanga.  
\v 3 Peni mundu ywohele ywanga kunyitikila Kilisto, kabhegha ng'obhe na aywo Nhuki ghwa Chapanga. Mundu aywo kabhegha na nhuki ghwa kunpingika Kilisto, na mwenga mukiyihwa kala kukita katahika npingika Kilisto, na hino kahika kala pannima. 
\p  
\v 4 Peni mwenga, ndo bhana bha Chapanga, na mwenga mubhahotola abho bhandu ahwangi kiyaha Nhuki ywakabheghite nkati yenu ndo nkulu kupitingana yula ywakabheghite nkati yabhe.  
\v 5 Bhombe bhangubhukana na milando ya munnima, nabho bhandu bha munnima bhanganyitikila kiyaha bhombe ndo bhandu bha nnima aghu.  
\v 6 Peni twenga ndo bhake Chapanga. Mundu ywohele ywaanmanyite Chapanga kangutuyihwa, mundu ywanga kubhegha na Chapanga kangutuyihwa ng'obhe. Basi kwa njila ayi twahotola kunmanya kafauti nkati ya Nhuki ghwa hoto na nhuki ghwa uhwangi. 
\s1 Chapanga ndo Upalo 
\p  
\v 7 Maalongo apalo, tupalane, kiyaha upalo ghunguhuma kwa Chapanga. Ywohele ywakabheghite na upala kabhelekwa na Chapanga, naywo kangunmanya Chapanga.  
\v 8 Yula ywanga kupala kangunmanya ng'obhe Chapanga, kiyaha Chapanga ndo upalo.  
\v 9 Na Chapanga kakighubhoneha upalo ghwaki kwa twenga kya kunlaghila mwana ghwaki ghwa kya ghweka munnima, ili kwa njila yake tumokole kulama.  
\v 10 Aghu ndo upalo ghwene, chepa twenga tuuyandite kumpala Chapanga, ngati kukita ywombe kakiyanda kutupala twenga mbaka kakinnaghila Mwana ghwake kabheghe nyambi ya kutubhuhila ulemwa ghwetu. 
\p  
\v 11 Maalongo apalo, handa Chapanga kakitupala habho, basi na twenga tungunoghwa tupalana twabhene.  
\v 12 Kahone mundu ywakammonite Chapanga, peni handa patupalana, Chapanga katatama papamu na twenga, na upalo ghwake ghwabhegha handa bhula Chapanga pakatupala twenga. 
\p  
\v 13 Tungumanya kukita tungutama papamu na Chapanga na ywombe Chapanga kangutama nkati yetu, kiyaha katupegha twenga kipalamande kya Nhuki ghwaki.  
\v 14 Na twenga tubhona na kulubhulila kukita Tate kakinnaghila Mwana ghwake ili kabheghe Nnopohi ghwa bhandu.  
\v 15 Ywohele ywakalongela na kuyitikila kukita Yesu ndo Mwana ghwa Chapanga, Chapanga kangutama papamu na ywombe, na ywombe kangutama papamu na Chapanga.  
\v 16 Habhu, twenga tungumanya na tunguhyubhalila kukita Chapanga kangutupala twenga. 
\p Chapanga ndo upalo. Ywohele ywakatama mu upalo aywo kangutama nkati ya Chapanga na Chapanga kangutama nkati yake.  
\v 17 Kwa njila ayi, Chapanga kangutwihiliha upalo ghwake nkati mwetu, ili tubheghe na ukangamalo mu linjubha lya kutoswa.  
\v 18 Paabheghite na upala kahone lyogha. Peni upalo ghwa hoto ghungubhingabhinga panje lyogha lyoha. Kiyaha kiituyingiha lyogha ndo mahwacho gha kutoswa. Ywohele ywakabhegha na lyoha kabhegha ng'obhe na upalo ghwa hoto. 
\p  
\v 19 Twenga tubhegha na upalo kiyaha Chapanga kakitupala kalongohi.  
\v 20 Handa mundu katalongela, “Nungumpala Chapanga.” Peni kangunkalalila nnongo ghwaki, aywo ndo nhwangi. Kiyaha mundu ywakanpala ng'obhe nnongo ghwake ywaammona, aywo kahone kunpala Chapanga ywene ywakammonite ng'obhe.  
\v 21 Hinu, ali ndo ngwiliho yakatupeghite Kilisto, ywohele yaanpala Chapanga kangunoghwa kupala nnyake. 
\c 5  
\s1 Kuhotola ulemwa mu nnima 
\p  
\v 1 Ywehele ywakahyubhalila kukita Yesu ndo Kilisto, aywo Mwana ghwa Chapanga, na ywohele yakampala Tate katampala bhubho mwana ghwake.  
\v 2 Kya abhu, tungumanya kukita tunguapala bhana bha Chapanga, kya kumpala Chapanga na kuyitikila malaghilo ghake.  
\v 3 Kiyaha kumpala Chapanga ndo kuyitikila ngwiliho yake na ngwiliho hyake chepa nonopo,  
\v 4 kiyaha ywohele ywakabhelekitwe na Chapanga kataghuhotola nnima. Na aku ndo mutughuhotola nnima, kwa kuhyubhalila kwetu.  
\v 5 Ndo ghani aywo ywakahotola ulemwa ghwa nnima? Ndo yula ywaahyubhalila kukita Yesu ndo Mwana ghwa Chapanga. 
\s1 Kuaghombela bhandu kwa mihalo ya Yesu 
\p  
\v 6 Yesu Kilisto ndo ywakahikite kwa machi gha ubatiso ghwake na mwahi ghwa kuhwegha kwake. Kakihika ng'obhe kwa machi ghweka, ngati kwa machi na mwahe. Naywo Nhuki ghwa Chapanga kangubhoneha kukita ndo hoto, kiyaha Nhuki ghwa Chapanga ndo uhoto.  
\v 7 Kiyaha abhegha andatu bhangututenda tumanye kukita Yesu kakihuma kwa Chapanga,  
\v 8 abho ndo Nhuki ghwa Chapanga, machi na mwahi, na abha bhoha andatu bhangulongela nnando ghulaghula kukita Yesu kahuma kwa Chapanga.  
\v 9 Tungubhahyubhalila bhandu paalongela nnando ghuubheghite hoto, peni kila kyakalongela Chapanga ndo kikulu kyanalumu, na ayi ndo Chapanga pakatughombelite, kakitughombela uhoto kwakya Mwana ghwake.  
\v 10 Ywohele ywakanhyubhalila Mwana ghwa Chapanga kabhegha na uhoto ghwakatughombela Chapanga, peni bhandu bhanga kunhyubhalila Chapanga bhanguntenda Chapanga kukita nhwangi, kiyaha bhanguhyubhalila ng'obhe kila Chapanga kakitughombela kwakya Mwana ghwake.  
\v 11 Na uhoto ghwene ndo aghu, Chapanga kakitupegha ubhumi ghwa manjubha ghoha, naghwo ubhumi aghwo ghubhegha mu Mwana ghwake.  
\v 12 Ywakabhegha na Mwana ghwa Chapanga kabhegha naghwo ubhumi aghwo, na ywanga kubhegha na Mwana ghwa Chapanga kubhegha ng'obhe na ubhumi. 
\s1 Ubhumi ghwa manjubha ghoha ghwanga uhiko 
\p  
\v 13 Nunguatyekela mwenga muulihyubhalila Lihina lya Mwana ghwa Chapanga ngati mmokole kumanya kukita mmegha na ubhumi ghwa manjubha ghoha ghwanga uhiko.  
\v 14 Twenga tubhegha ng'obhe na lyogha mu ulongolo ghwa Chapanga kiyaha tungumanya kukita handa patunnyupa kyohele tela na pakapala ywombe, katatuyihwa.  
\v 15 Twenga tungumanya kukita kangutuyihwa patunnyupa kyohele, na kangi tungumanya kukita kangutupegha kyohele kitunnyupa. 
\p  
\v 16 Handa mundu kammona nnongo ghwake kangutenda ulemwa ghwanga kunnyambuha kahweghe, kangunoghwa kannyupile kwa Chapanga, naywo Chapanga katanpegha ubhumi mundu aywo. Nungulongela malagho agha kwa bhandu bhala bhaatenda ulemwa ghwanga kuayambuha ahweghe. Peni ghubhegha ulemwa ghuunnyambuha mundu kahweghe, na nenga nungulongela ng'obhe kukita kangunoghwa kunnyupa Chapanga kwakya aghwo.  
\v 17 Ndendelo ywohele yanga kunnogheha Chapanga ndo ulemwa, peni ghubha ulemwa ghuuntendite ng'obhe mundu kahweghe. 
\p  
\v 18 Tungumanya kukita ywohele Chapanga kangutenda ng'obhe ulemwa kiyaha mwana ywa Chapaknga kangunkingikiha tela, ebu yula nhakata kahotola ng'obhe kunntendela uhakata. 
\p  
\v 19 Twenga tungumanya kukita tubha bhana bha Chapanga, peni nnima ghoha ghubhegha mu utabhala bha yula Nchipila. 
\p  
\v 20 Kangi tungumanya kukita Mwana ghwa Chapanga kahika, naywo katupegha twenga mahala ngati tumokole kummanya Chapanga ywa hoto. Na twenga tubhegha na ughumu na Chapanga ghwa hoto kiyaha tubhegha na ughumu na Mwana ghwake, Aywo ndo Chapanga ghwa hoto ndo ywkatupegha ubhumi ghwa manjubhaghoh ghanga uhiko. 
\p  
\v 21 Bhana apalo, ntame kutali na machapanga!